// Minimal reshape: map one Python parse-tree construct to an AST node.
// Demonstrates mapping FuncDef -> FuncDefAST (step 2 of the rewrite-for-Python plan).
// No @type needed for this test; we just build a node with the same child.

reshape <~ FuncDef(Child: ?c) -> FuncDefAST(Child: ?c)
        / ?x -> ?x
